; Keep npm's legacy (npm@6) peer-dependency behavior so installs are not refused
; on peerOptional / peer version mismatches across our dependency tree. We rely
; on `overrides` in package.json to pin the transitive versions we actually need.
; NOTE: this is a repo-wide setting and will silence ALL peer-dependency
; conflicts, so review `npm install` warnings when adding/upgrading deps.
legacy-peer-deps=true
